help.descr:
        The function implements call to LINPROG solver based on formulation from Opt class.
        Only LP problems are supported.

        It is assumed that LP entering this function is of the form

			\begin{eqnarray}
  				\min &&  {f}^{T}x \label{eq:linprog:QP0-obj} \\
				\text{s.t.}  && \text{lb} \le x \le  \text{ub}  \label{eq:linprog:QP0-ineq1} \\
                && Ax \le  b  \label{eq:linprog:QP0-ineq2}\\
				&& {A}_{e}x = {b}_{e} \label{eq:linprog:QP0-eq}
            \end{eqnarray} 

        which is passed to LINPROG solver directly.
